  "markdown": "[![Quantum Dice Logo](https://quantum-dice.com/QuantumDice_Logo_Light_Mode.svg)](https://quantum-dice.com/)\n[Technology](https://quantum-dice.com/technology)\n[Products](https://quantum-dice.com/products)\n[Resources](https://quantum-dice.com/resources)\n[Get in Touch [1]](https://quantum-dice.com/contact)[Try ORBIT\u2122 [2]](https://quantum-dice.com/)\n# Trust Centre\nTransparency and security are at the heart of everything we do. Learn about our certifications, policies, and commitments to protecting your data and privacy.\n## Certifications\nOur security certifications and compliance standards.\n![ISO 27001 logo](https://quantum-dice.com/api/images/trust-center/1773362398200-BAB-ISO-cropped.png)\n### ISO 27001\nInformation Security Management System certification ensuring the highest standards of data protection.\n![Cyber Essentials logo](https://quantum-dice.com/api/images/trust-center/1781170026831-Cyber-Essentials-Logo-v2.png)\n### Cyber Essentials\nCyber Essentials is the highest level of certification offered under the UK government-backed Cyber Essentials scheme. \n## Policies\nOur policies ensure transparency and compliance with industry standards.\n### Privacy Policy\nHow we collect, use, and protect your personal information\n### Cookie Policy\nInformation about cookies and similar technologies we use\n## Subprocessors\nThird-party services we use to process data on your behalf.\n### Plus Five Five, Inc.\nUnited States\nEmail Notifications\nManage email notifications from contact forms on the website\n### Supabase\nSweden\nDatabase & Authentication\nDatabase management and user authentication\n### Google Ireland Limited\nUnited States\nAnalytics\nAnalyses website traffic and visitor behaviour. Only active after cookie consent.\n### BambooHR\nUnited Kingdom\nHR Management\nRecruitment and HR processes\n### Microsoft Ireland Operations Limited\nIreland\nMicrosoft Clarity\nSession recordings and heatmaps to improve usability. No keystrokes or form inputs captured. Only active after cookie consent.\n### Functional Software Inc\nGermany\nError Analytics\nError monitoring and performance tracking to maintain website reliability. Operates under legitimate interest without cookie consent. Data processed in the EU.\n## Updates\nRecent changes to our security and compliance posture.\n### Privacy Policy Update\n3/22/2026\nUpdated our Privacy Policy to include new data processing activities and enhanced user rights.\n![Quantum Dice Logo](https://quantum-dice.com/QuantumDice_Logo_Light_Mode.svg)\n\u00a9 2026 Quantum Dice Limited. All rights reserved.\n### Technology\n  * [Overview](https://quantum-dice.com/technology/overview)\n  * [Applications](https://quantum-dice.com/technology/applications)\n\n\n### Products\n  * [ORBIT PPU](https://quantum-dice.com/products/orbit-processors)\n  * [DISC QRNGs](https://quantum-dice.com/products/qrng)\n\n\n### Resources\n  * [All Resources](https://quantum-dice.com/resources)\n  * [Blog](https://quantum-dice.com/resources?category=Blog)\n  * [Research Papers](https://quantum-dice.com/resources?category=Research)\n  * [White Papers](https://quantum-dice.com/resources?category=White%20Papers)\n\n\n### Company\n  * [About Us](https://quantum-dice.com/about)\n  * [Contact](https://quantum-dice.com/contact)\n  * [Careers](https://quantum-dice.com/careers)\n  * [Trust Centre](https://quantum-dice.com/trust-center)\n  * [Try ORBIT](https://quantum-dice.com/)\n\n\nWe use cookies to enhance your experience. By continuing to visit this site you agree to our use of cookies. [Learn more](https://quantum-dice.com/trust-center)\nRejectAccept\n",
